narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: That we need to be creative and innovative people. We need to ask the question that has not been asked before and try and make things surrounding us better.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Overall I really enjoyed the critical and creative thinking class. Maybe more projects like the last one we need where we needed to find a solution to an actual problem could be great.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! critical and creative thinking should be something we do constantly in our daily lives. We need to develop and awake our minds.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
How will you use the knowledge and skills you learned in this course in your future endeavors?
comments: Daily! I think is an important part of our developing and innovative world that we practise this everyday.
